          <li><strong>System Metrics:</strong> Server activity logs, performance statistics</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>4.2 Data Storage</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>PostgreSQL:</strong> Primary user data and configurations</li>
          <li><strong>Redis:</strong> Temporary cache data and sessions</li>
          <li><strong>Pinecone:</strong> AI vectors for content analysis</li>
          <li><strong>SQLite:</strong> Local functions and temporary data</li>
          <li><strong>MongoDB:</strong> NEBULA BOT operational data</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>4.3 Geographic Location</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>European servers for ARCHAN JS BOT and NEBULA BOT</li>
          <li>US servers for SAKURA IA BOT</li>
          <li>Geographic optimization to reduce latency</li>
        </ul>

