          <li><strong>Level 0.9:</strong> Gemini 1.5 Pro (Legacy compatibility)</li>
          <li><strong>Level 1:</strong> DeepSeek R1 (Advanced reasoning via OpenRouter)</li>
          <li><strong>Level 2:</strong> OpenAI (Reliable backup)</li>
          <li><strong>Level 3:</strong> Enhanced kawaii programming responses</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>5.2 AI Limitations</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Responses are limited to 2000 characters due to Discord restrictions</li>
          <li>Cooldown systems: AI (30s), Social (10s) per user</li>
          <li>Administrators can override cooldown limitations</li>
          <li>Intelligent truncation is applied automatically</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>5.3 Multimodal Capabilities</h3>
        <ul>
